title: Olympus 01-04 (of 4|Image|2009|c2c-1280) (DCP + Minutemen scans)
description:
Promotional description:

 " In ancient Greece, Zeus granted eternal life to two brothers, and bound them to
   his service. 3,000 years later, they are hunting an exiled god, only in their
   hunt they release onto earth one of Hades' most dangerous prisoners. With a
   fresh, compelling visual style and original storytelling, 'Olympus' is a rebirth
   of classical mythology into action and intrigue. " 

  -- <a href=" https://imagecomics.com/comics/series/olympus" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> https://imagecomics.com/comics/series/olympus</a>


Contains:

   Olympus 01-04 (of 04) (2009) (c2c) (neverwhere-DCP)
   Olympus 01-04 (of 04) (2009) (c2c) (Minutemen)

    ( the Minutemen releases were, as usual, the higher-quality scans, but many
      pages, particularly in the first two issues, are both quite dark and a bit
      overcropped - see examples below - so I decided to include both sets here )
